      "id": "",
      "name": "Mindlock",
      "legend": "",
      "factionId": "",
      "description": "While a <span class=\"tooltip00434\" data-tooltip-content=\"#tooltip_content00434\" data-tooltip-anchor=\"#tooltip_content00434\"><span class=\"kwb\">TECH-PRIEST</span></span> model is leading this unit, improve the Ballistic Skill and Weapon Skill characteristics of ranged and melee weapons equipped by <span class=\"kwb\">SERVITOR</span> models in this unit by 1.",
      "type": "Datasheet",
